    button.button-green.big &#10004; Your Tweet4me is setup
    p.margin-top-big 
      a.underline(href="/tweet4me/feed?user={{email}}") View your Tweet4me feed.
    p.margin-top-big 
      | If you need help, please reach out to us at 
      a.underline(href="mailto:admin@buzzr.io") admin@buzzr.io


